title: 10/07/21 DPS Hour 2 Mike Lowell and Steve Palazzolo
itunes:title: 10/07/21 DPS Hour 2 Mike Lowell and Steve Palazzolo
description:
MLB Network analyst Mike Lowell joins the show to talk MLB playoffs, and PFF analyst Steve Palazzolo joins the show ahead of tonight's game between the Rams and the Seahawks and tells you why he'd take Russell Wilson over Matthew Stafford.
